{
  "stem": "18626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that was by a woman who knew all the people in Slobodka, especially on [INAUDIBLE] Gasse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my grandmother tell me that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say it was pure luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we would have lived on [INAUDIBLE] Gasse, we would have been slaughtered the same thing like the thousands other Jews were slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we lived at the outskirts between a lot of, you know, factories was a all around there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe we were saved, but it was a time my mother got scared already too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she start, you know to separate some of us, the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the beginning, we thought that it's going to be more safe-- safer to live in the Jewish section than in the Gentile where we lived, you know, on the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So for a couple of days, my mother sent me away to my grandmother to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was actually a day before the pogram, a day or two days before the pograms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Germans were already in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, when I was in my grandmother's, when I was in my grandmother's house, sleep over the night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was May, I mean, that was June the 26th.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got up-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was the 25th, I'm sorry, 25th in the morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I heard, you know, noise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went in my grandmother's yard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a ball, like a soccer ball, over the fence fell in right in my grandmother's yard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I look at the ball, and I opened up the gate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw all the trucks, the German trucks, the army trucks, and all ammunitions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the all, the part of the German army was already in [INAUDIBLE] Gasse.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
